thin 5 days from the date that you physically receive the products.</li><li style="text-align: justify;">We will refund or exchange any products that are returned in resalable condition with a copy of your original invoice.</li><li style="text-align: justify;">Refunds for returned orders will be issued to the original form of payment less the delivery fee and VAT. For exchanged orders, any price difference from the original order will either be credited to or debited from the original payment method used to place the order.</li><li style="text-align: justify;">All returned items must be in a new and unused condition, with all original tags and labels attached.</li></ul></li></ol><p></p><ul></ul><p></p><h4 style="text-align: justify;">Right to Cancel</h4>
